content:
The trip plan involves visiting Dublin first for 2 days, then flying to Riga on the same day as the departure from Dublin (Day 2), staying in Riga for 5 days including the arrival day, and finally flying to Vilnius on the same day as the departure from Riga (Day 6), staying in Vilnius for 7 days until Day 12. This sequence uses the available direct flights: Dublin to Riga and Riga to Vilnius. The flight days (Day 2 and Day 6) are counted for both the departure and arrival cities, ensuring the total stay days match the requirements (Dublin: 2 days, Riga: 5 days, Vilnius: 7 days) within the 12-day trip.

